<h2>2. Data Collected</h2>
<p>This website is static and <strong>does not directly collect personal data</strong>. We do not use profiling cookies, tracking tools, or contact forms.</p>
<p>The hosting provider (Netlify, Inc.) may automatically collect technical data such as IP address, browser type, and pages visited through its access logs, solely to ensure the operation and security of the site.</p>

<h2>3. Third-party Services</h2>
<h3>Netlify (hosting)</h3>
<p>This site is hosted on Netlify, Inc. (USA). Netlify may process technical browsing data for security and operational purposes. For more information: <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Netlify Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

<h3>Calendly (bookings)</h3>
<p>To book a free call, the user is redirected to the Calendly platform (Calendly, LLC — USA). Data entered in Calendly is processed according to <a href="https://calendly.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Calendly's Privacy Policy</a>. The Data Controller does not have direct access to data collected by Calendly other than what is necessary to manage the appointment.</p>

<h2>4. Cookies</h2>
<p>This site <strong>does not use its own cookies</strong>. Technical cookies may be set by the hosting provider (Netlify) for the operation of the site.</p>

<h2>5. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
<p>The processing of technical browsing data by the hosting provider is based on the <strong>legitimate interest</strong> of the Data Controller in ensuring the operation and security of the site (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR).</p>

<h2>6. Data Transfers Outside the EU</h2>
<p>The hosting (Netlify) and booking (Calendly) services are based in the United States. Data transfers to the USA are carried out on the basis of safeguards provided by the EU-U.S. Data Privacy Framework or Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs).</p>

<h2>7. Rights of the Data Subject</h2>
<p>Under Articles 15-22 of the GDPR, users have the right to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Access their personal data</li>
  <li>Request rectification or erasure</li>
  <li>Restrict or object to processing</li>
  <li>Request data portability</li>
  <li>Lodge a complaint with the Italian Data Protection Authority (<a href="https://www.garanteprivacy.it" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.garanteprivacy.it</a>)</li>
</ul>
<p>To exercise your rights, contact the Data Controller at: <a href="mailto:ellev.artcoach@gmail.com">ellev.artcoach@gmail.com</a></p>

